<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>ARYZEL CREATION HOUSE</title>

<style>
    body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        background-color #pink;
    }

    /* HEADER */
    header {
        background-color: aqua;
        height: 250px;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 0 0 20px 20px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    header img {
        width: 80px;
        border-radius: 50%;
    }

    header h1 {
        margin-top: 10px;
        color: black;
    }

    /* SECTION */
    section {
        background-color: whitesmoke;
        margin: 20px;
        padding: 20px;
        border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .text-style {
        text-align: center;
        color: darkblue;
        font-size: 18px;
    }

    .section-text {
        color: #333;
        text-align: justify;
    }

    /* FOOTER */
    footer {
        background-color: black;
        color: white;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 15px;
        margin-top: 20px;
    }

</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
    <img src="Tesla Laptops/Downloads/WhatsApp Image 2026-02-06 at 4.27.41 PM.jpeg" alt="Logo AC">
    <h1>My Website Header</h1>
</header>

<section>
    <h2 class="text-style">Welcome ARYZEL STORE</h2>
    
    <p class="section-text">
        This is FOR U. Here you caN BUY ANYTHING YOU WANT. 
        This store give u branded variety in cheapest price.
    </p>

    <p class="text-style">
        Join with us and enjoy ur shopping.
    </p>
</section>

<footer>
    <p>© 2026 My Website | All Rights Reserved</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>